{"lastModified":1753568327244,"uri":"c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-822f-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae","yachtType":["Catamaran","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nRoyal Cracow is one of the most luxurious and modern catamarans on the Adriatic Sea managed by enthusiastic Polish owners. In his category belongs to TOP 3 best catamarans in Croatia available for charter. In hotel terminology, this catamaran is a floating 5***** hotel. This elegant beauty on the water and with high levels of performance, also offers a splendid place to relax with its carefully crafted Lounge deck. This is integrated into the design process from the very beginning in order to give the craft its beautiful lines as well as the best possible levels of comfort, both at sea and at mooring. Motion on board has been designed to ensure privacy between saloon, front or rear deck or Lounge deck on the top floor. Royal Cracow is ideal for multigeneration families, students and young people which wish to experience unforgettable sailing party. Alternatively it can perfectly fit for business partners arranging teambuilding for their clients and employees.\n\nTo bring you feeling of exclusivity, uniqueness and novelty, we performed for you complete reconstruction of interior and exterior early 2025.","blueprint":{"name":"ROYAL CRACOW","images":["/media/media::image::c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-822f-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae::assets::f9bbb1e0-8231-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-822f-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae::assets::c9a3e050-1489-11ef-a805-7b2c3c9892e0.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-822f-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae::assets::fe83e850-8231-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-822f-11ee-bb51-976bcca658ae::assets::831d1820-884f-11ee-bf65-2d8f77227005.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10218162598::vessel::d7559cd0-82